<center>
<h1> Welcome to Loot-List! </h1><br><br>
  <P> Just last week somewhere in this world, a wife asked her husband what he would like for his birthday.  Not expecting anything more than the usual response.....</P><br>

  <p> This usual response is sweet and just what a wife wants to hear (not in this case!)....</p><br>

  <p> Herein lies the perfect solution......private, secure, available to loved ones, family, friends....form groups...  Info always there and easily updated to</p><br>

